ham and split pea soup

1 bag dried split peas (flat)
rince them
drain

sautee lrg fine chopped onion
2tbs butter
little salte

add minced garlic
add 7 cups water

add 1 thick ham steak
3 strips of of american bacon
2 bay leaves
2 sprigs tymes

add peas 
simmer ~45 minutes 
(until peas are tender not splitting/breaking)

``````
remove the ham steak
shred ham with fork

add diced carrot and celery 
further simmer for ~30 minutes
discard bacon
readd shredded ham back

top mith small garlic crutons
and mint
